t is fulfilled.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-21T08:22:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Project Manager (advisory function)","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-07-15T14:16:04Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Selvarani Elahi - Project Manager (advisory function)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"d0b5c245-e47e-44b8-a33c-b38f517b164d","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2056,"started_on":"2011-06-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8475442c-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>Nominated officers have the overall responsibility for referee case supervision and prepare and sign Government Chemist certificates of analysis. They must hold the statutory Mastership in Chemical Analysis qualification to act as referee analyst.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T15:25:37Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Nominated Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-06-07T14:20:47Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Selvarani Elahi - Nominated Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"3948a759-5262-43c5-a973-f8a44be70344","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2048,"started_on":"2011-06-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"847542d0-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Deputy Government Chemist deputises for the Government Chemist, advising on food and agricultural analysis and authorises certificates of analysis for referee cases in his absence.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T14:13:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Government Chemist","wi