 of analytical science and technology and providing advice to Government on policy standards, regulation based on research carried out by him and his team.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"chief_scientific_advisor_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T13:50:48Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Government Chemist","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84754144-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Principal Scientist helps advise the Government Chemist on best measurement practice guidelines for using molecular biology approaches for food authenticity testing and investigating food fraud. The role includes advising on the maintenance of core technologies and developing improved methods for detection, identification and quantitation of animal and plant species in food.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T13:58:31Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Principal Scientist and Special Advisor","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"847542d0-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Deputy Government Chemist deputises for the Government Chemist, advising on food and agricultural analysis and authorises certificates of analysis for referee cases in his absence.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T14:13:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Government Chemist","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84754332-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Analysis Manager is responsible for the analysis of food and feed submitted to the Government Chemist, and also for managing projects aimed at developing the measurement capability of the Government Chemist.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T14:54:00Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Analysis Manager","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8475438a-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Science Manager is responsible for using their experience to benefit the Government Chemist programme. They improve how research findings are shared with government, the public, and the food and feed industry.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T17:00:43Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Consultant Science Manager","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"847543db-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>Nominated officers have the overall responsibility for referee case supervision and prepare and sign Government Chemist certificates of analysis. Holding the statutory Mastership in Chemical Analysis qualification (MChemA), Paul acts as referee analyst leading on and managing the majority of referee cases.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-04-21T15:59:18Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Referee Analyst and Nominated Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8475442c-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>Nominated officers have the overall responsibility for referee case supervision and prepare and sign Government Chemist certificates of analysis. They must hold the statutory Mastership in Chemical Analysis qualification to act as referee analyst.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-17T15:25:37Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Nominated Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84754a2a-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Project Manager is responsible for ensuring the advisory function of the Government Chemist is fulfilled.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-21T08:22:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Project Manager (advisory function)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"84754a7a-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Programme Manager oversees the delivery of the programme and reports progress to the National Measurement Office and its advisory working group.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-07-21T08:25:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Programme Manager","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7c93c824-3abf-480e-81f5-86fe83a0ab44","details":{"body":"<p>As head of OGC Paul looks after a team of senior scientists who in turn are responsible for program management, delivery of referee casework, and the work of the Food and Consumer Products Testing unit which includes National Reference Laboratory (NRL) responsibilities.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-05-11T16:48:10Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Head of the Office of the Government Chemist (OGC)","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1061","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/government-chemist","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/government-chemist","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-chemist","content_id":"9748e764-3ea4-4f58-bf1c-656970401a22","details":{"acronym":"Government Chemist","brand":"department-for-business-innovation-skills","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/681cac283f1c73824ee3e5d7/s960_GClogo_scales_TudorCrown_Black-03-03.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/681cac29e26cd2f713d870dc/s300_GClogo_scales_TudorCrown_Black-03-03.png"},"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Government Chemist","image":{"alt_text":"Government Chemist","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/681cac2943d6699b3c1d2a55/GClogo_TudorCrown_Black-01.png"}},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Government Chemist","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-chemist","withdrawn":false}],"primary_publishing_organisation":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1061","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/government-chemist","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/government-chemist","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-chemist","content_id":"9748e764-3ea4-4f58-bf1c-656970401a22","details":{"acronym":"Government Chemist","brand":"department-for-business-innovation-skills","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/681cac283f1c73824ee3e5d7/s960_GClogo_scales_TudorCrown_Black-03-03.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/681cac29e26cd2f713d870dc/s300_GClogo_scales_TudorCrown_Black-03-03.png"},"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Government Chemist","image":{"alt_text":"Government Chemist","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/681cac2943d6699b3c1d2a55/GClogo_TudorCrown_Black-01.png"}},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Government Chemist","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-chemist","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","phase":"live","public_updated_at":"2025-05-08T14:05:44+01:00","publishing_app":"whitehall","publishing_request_id":"21-1775809005.649-10.13.20.149-3210","publishing_scheduled_at":null,"rendering_app":"collections","scheduled_publishing_delay_seconds":null,"schema_name":"organisation","title":"Government Chemist","updated_at":"2026-05-14T17:11:38+01:00","withdrawn_notice":{}}